Use the min and profit variables

min is used get track of the smallest value in the array till the traversal

profit is used find the max profit till current .Profit=current-min


class Solution {
    public int maxProfit(int[] prices) 
    {

        int min=Integer.MAX_VALUE;
        int profit=0;

        for(int i=0;i<prices.length;i++)
        {
            min=Math.min(min,prices[i]);
            profit=Math.max(profit,prices[i]-min);

        }
        return profit;
        
    }
}

Time Complexity:O(N)
Space Complexity:O(1)